Parties
Hosting your event at
Evie’s
is almost as easy as just showing up. Whether you’re planning a birthday party, a fundraiser, or a corporate event, our event specialists will work with you to ensure that it’s an affair to remember. Let us help you with your next event, we’ll take care of all the details and you can sit back, relax and enjoy your party. To start the process, take a look at the packages below and fill out an information request. Once received, an event specialist will get in touch with you.
Details
You must provide supervision throughout your whole event (at all times)
You can bring your own cupcakes or birthday cake. (you will need to provide plates and cutlery)
There must be one adult per eight children on the mini-golf course
An 20% gratuity will be added
We will help you create a package that all your guest will have fun and love!
Start Planning Your Party Today!
